OL,3,CThames Water receives buyout offer
OL,4,Cfrom investment group Covalis Capital
OL,6,FInvestment firm Covalis Capital has
OL,7,Fmade an offer for Thames Water, in a
OL,8,Fplan which could see the embattled
OL,9,Futility giant broken up into smaller
OL,10,Fbusinesses.
OL,12,FCovalis's bid involves bringing in
OL,13,FFrench company Suez to help it run
OL,14,FThames Water as it sells off large
OL,15,Fchunks of the supplier's assets.
OL,17,FThe offer involves #1 billion up
OL,18,Ffront, plus another #4 billion from
OL,19,Fplanned asset sales and refinancing.
