OL,3,CThames Water receives buyout offer
OL,4,Cfrom investment group Covalis Capital
OL,6,FThe sales could include selling
OL,7,Findividual pieces of infrastructure
OL,8,Fsuch as tunnels, then leasing them
OL,9,Fback.
OL,11,FBut they could also involve hiving off
OL,12,Fentire regions that Thames Water
OL,13,Fserves, such as the Thames Valley.
OL,15,FThe new owner would then list what
OL,16,Fremains of Thames Water on the stock
OL,17,Fmarket.
OL,19,FCovalis is a utility investment firm.
