OL,3,CThames Water receives buyout offer
OL,4,Cfrom investment group Covalis Capital
OL,6,FIt has interests in major
OL,7,Finfrastructure groups across Europe
OL,8,Fsuch as German energy giant RWE.
OL,10,FSuez, meanwhile, runs major water
OL,11,Fservices in France and has about 5,000
OL,12,Fworkers in the UK.
OL,14,FIt would act in an advisory role,
OL,15,Fhelping current management to overhaul
OL,16,FThames Water's operations and
OL,17,Finstalling things such as more up-to-
OL,18,Fdate IT and leak monitoring systems.
OL,20,FHowever, Suez would not own any shares
OL,21,Fin Thames Water.
