OL,3,CThames Water receives buyout offer
OL,4,Cfrom investment group Covalis Capital
OL,6,FThe Government would hold a so-called
OL,7,Fgolden share in the company, giving it
OL,8,Fa seat on the board and other rights.
OL,10,FCovalis's bid is not thought to depend
OL,11,Fon bill hikes as steep as those
OL,12,Frequested by Thames Water's current
OL,13,Fmanagement.
OL,15,FThames Water has asked regulator Ofwat
OL,16,Fto let it raise average bills by 53%
OL,17,Fover the next five years, compared
OL,18,Fwith current levels.
