OL,3,CThames Water receives buyout offer
OL,4,Cfrom investment group Covalis Capital
OL,6,FHowever, the bid is dependent on Ofwat
OL,7,Fallowing Thames Water to slow a
OL,8,Frequired programme of investment in
OL,9,Fupgrading its infrastructure and
OL,10,Fsystems for the next few years, which
OL,11,Fbidders are thought to view as
OL,12,Funachievable.
OL,14,FOfwat will give its final verdict on
OL,15,FThames Water's five-year business plan
OL,16,Fon December 19, including proposals
OL,17,Ffor customer bill hikes and investment.
OL,19,FA spokesperson for Suez confirmed that
OL,20,Fit had entered an "exclusive
OL,21,Fpartnership" with Covalis on the bid.
