OL,3,CThames Water receives buyout offer
OL,4,Cfrom investment group Covalis Capital
OL,6,FThames Water, which is the UK's
OL,7,Fbiggest water supplier, had asked
OL,8,Fpossible investors to put forward
OL,9,Findicative bids by the end of Thursday
OL,10,FDecember 5.
OL,12,FThe utility giant is looking to secure
OL,13,Fa multibillion-pound cash injection to
OL,14,Fstave off nationalisation.
OL,16,FOther possible investors preparing to
OL,17,Fput in bids reportedly include Hong
OL,18,FKong firm CK Infrastructure Holdings
OL,19,Fand private equity giant KKR, which
OL,20,Ftogether own stakes in Northumbrian
OL,21,FWater.
