OL,3,CThames Water receives buyout offer
OL,4,Cfrom investment group Covalis Capital
OL,6,FIt is thought that Thames Water and
OL,7,Fits adviser Rothschild have also
OL,8,Fsounded out investment giants
OL,9,FBrookfield Asset Management and
OL,10,FCarlyle Group.
OL,12,FThames Water, which serves about 16
OL,13,Fmillion people, is in the grip of a
OL,14,Ffunding crisis and only has enough
OL,15,Fcash to continue operating until early
OL,16,Fnext year.
OL,18,FIt needs at least #3.3 billion in
OL,19,Fequity over the next five years, while
OL,20,Fit is also more than #16 billion in
OL,21,Fdebt.
