OL,3,CThames Water receives buyout offer
OL,4,Cfrom investment group Covalis Capital
OL,6,FAs well as seeking to raise equity,
OL,7,FThames is also in the middle of a debt
OL,8,Frestructuring and recently appointed
OL,9,FJulian Gething ` a director of
OL,10,Fturnaround firm Alix Partners ` as
OL,11,Fchief restructuring officer to oversee
OL,12,Fthe process.
OL,14,FThames Water still needs the emergency
OL,15,Ffunding plans to be passed in court
OL,16,Fthough, and is aiming for a December
OL,17,F17 hearing.
OL,19,FCovalis and Thames Water declined to
OL,20,Fcomment.
